-- Billionaire Zyuzin Sells 2% of Russia’s Mechel, Company Says
-- B y   J a c k   J o r d a n
-- 2012-07-16T17:49:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-16/billionaire-zyuzin-sells-2-of-russia-s-mechel-company-says.html
Billionaire Igor Zyuzin sold about 2
percent of OAO  Mechel (MTLR) , Russia’s largest producer of coal for
steelmakers, in a private deal this month, according to a
regulatory filing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
